title: Colin Kaepernick, others offer positive signs in 49ers’ victory
text:
Photo: Scott Strazzante, The Chronicle San Francisco 49ers' Colin Kaepernick passes in 1st quarter against Baltimore Ravens during NFL game at Levi's Stadium in Santa Clara, Calif., on Sunday, October 18, 2015. San Francisco 49ers' Colin Kaepernick passes in 1st quarter against...
The 49ers snapped their four-game losing streak Sunday and in the process, might have snapped back to life. And perhaps snapped their quarterback into sync.
